{
  "stem": "9415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from Dorohucha, being there a couple months seems like the SS send a message to the Dorohucha Germans and all over to Poland and all other camps that the people who worked in Warsaw in the printing-- they have a list of 39 people-- that time-- no, that time was already 120 people in the printing-- on the end.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on this list were now our names, and they would call out these names in Dorohucha.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took us out, me and my wife, and a couple more people were brought in this-- were in our group among the workers of this printing in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of this group, I don't remember how many there were, maybe eight or 10 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They send us to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was the place where of all camps, the people who worked and the printing supposed to come together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we all came together after-- it took another week or so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took us-- the train-- to Radom, where the printing is, the new printing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All the people from other camps came together in this place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In all the camps and all the place, we were together till later on, when the Russians were marching-- marching to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They closed the printing in Radom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took us on the way to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Radom was a small place, and we had an apartment outside the printing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to morning to work, and evening we went to sleep in the apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no life in Radom, no community life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all to it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we printed all these stuff for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Police-- orders, you know, the-- not to shoot-- shoot so many people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How's it called?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] publications.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How do you call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
